ActCanada Pension Plan Investment Board Act
PrecisAppointment of ASHLEIGH EVERETT of Winnipeg, Manitoba to be a director of the board of directors of the Canada Pension Plan Investment Board, to hold office during good behaviour for a term of three years, in the place of Nancy E. Hopkins, effective February 13, 2017.
